{"tid":957643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國人攜疫區肉品 明年1月起或不准入台","createTime":"2018-12-27T07:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T08:49:08.000Z","uid":77196,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5219f6c6b289d2d96675d301c9f17d39534db3db","tid":957643,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T07:36:51.000Z","msg":"台灣農委會今日表示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為避免外籍旅客違規攜帶疫區肉品入境，將研究2019年1月不准入境</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n農委會副主委李退之表示，中國大陸8月爆發非洲豬瘟，鄰國有口蹄疫、禽流感等疫情，為嚇阻旅客入境違規攜入疫區動物產品，罰款陸續提高。<br />\n<br />\n農委會動植物防疫檢疫局長馮海東表示，農委會着手了解各種疫情在國際上受認定的嚴重程度，綜合研析後先訂定執法原則，再依據原則列出從哪些疫情的疫區、帶入什麼產品的旅客應予禁止入境。"},{"pid":"93491195f89f71673e763973b26c1c8bfc321a88","tid":957643,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T07:38:22.000Z","msg":"睇黎好撚大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港食環漁護wfc?"},{"pid":"d2b741ae049460cf2ae6eb0f15c3cc8457edfb58","tid":957643,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcc546a39d31afd6490be7e30c313bab92420fc4","tid":957643,"uid":37463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93491195f89f71673e763973b26c1c8bfc321a88","tid":957643,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T07:38:22.000Z","msg":"睇黎好撚大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港食環漁護wfc?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T07:44:22.000Z","msg":"緊係大鑊 , 講緊本土豬會絕種"},{"pid":"a409b269651b27a5579b3a430d475b173fb9616d","tid":957643,"uid":184